-- German Coalition May Auction Reactor-Life Extensions, FT Deutschland Says
-- Jann Bettinga
-- 2010-07-13T02:01:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/german-coalition-may-auction-reactor-life-extensions-ft-deutschland-says.html

          
          
             German Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s
coalition is considering auctioning off operating-life
extensions for nuclear reactors, the  Financial Times Deutschland 
reported.  
 “This is an interesting proposal that deserves a serious
examination,” the newspaper cited Environment Minister  Norbert Roettgen  as saying in an e-mailed preview of a report to be
published in today’s edition.  
